      <title>中国调查欧盟白酒，贸易争端加剧导致股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/china-starts-anti-dumping-probe-on-brandy-from-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在对来自欧盟的白兰地等酒类产品发起反倾销调查，这是继去年秋天欧盟对其电动汽车补贴展开调查之后采取的相对温和的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/china-starts-anti-dumping-probe-on-brandy-from-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 07:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在美国就业数据公布之前，债券和股票继续下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/stocks-bonds-fall-as-investors-pare-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于劳动力市场的弹性可能会推迟美联储降息的猜测，美国国债延续跌势，将出现 10 月份以来最大单周回落。股市下跌，美元连续第六天走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/stocks-bonds-fall-as-investors-pare-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
